document.full_text: china has agreed to immediately provide 50 jf-17 fighter jets to pakistan, a major outcome of a visit by prime minister yousaf raza gilani to beijing this week, pakistani officials said thursday.
document.title: china gives pakistan 50 fighter jets
lines_and_colors: china has agreed to immediately provide 50 jf-17 fighter jets to pakistan, a major outcome of a visit by prime minister yousaf raza gilani to beijing this week, pakistani officials said thursday.
